      • testDeleteTable

        public void testDeleteTable()
        This test method deletes a table. As a waiter (default login defined in application.properties) does not have the permission to do so, a workaround is needed to login as member "chief". Do not try to delete table 101 as is has an attached order and will fail with error code 400.

      • testSaveTable

        public void testSaveTable()
        This test method creates a table using TableEtoBuilder and saves it into the database. As a waiter (default login defined in application.properties) does not have the permission to do so, a workaround is needed to login as member "chief".
